/home/jhimy/proyects/migrar-back-servici.serviceRawFile:
service: service-analysts
org: ${env:ORG}

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.9
  memorySize: 1024
  timeout: 29
  role: ${env:ROLE}
  environment:
    DATABASE_URL: ${env:DATABASE_URL}
    MY_DATABASE_NAME: ${env:MY_DATABASE_NAME}

package:
  individually: true
  exclude:
    - .serverless/**
    - .venv/**
    - .idea/**
    - financial-data/**
    - build_layer.sh
    - user/**
    - variables/**
    - businesses_businessId_ai-parse/**
    - "*.zip" #eres incluir otros ZIP que no sean necesarios
    - README.md  # Ejemplo, si hay archivos de documentacin que no necesitas

# Definicin del layer que contiene las dependencias comunes.
layers:
  commonLib:
    package:
      artifact: layer_common_lib.zip
    description: "Dependencias comunes para todas las Lambdas"

functions:
  analysts-get:
    handler: analysts/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts
          method: get
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - GET
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_create:
    handler: analysts_create/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/create
          method: post
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - POST
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_id_delete:
    handler: analysts_id_delete/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/{id}
          method: delete
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - DELETE
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_id_get:
    handler: analysts_id_get/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/{id}
          method: get
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - GET
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_id_patch:
    handler: analysts_id_patch/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/{id}
          method: patch
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - PATCH
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_id_assign-business:
    handler: analysts_id_assign-business/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/{id}/assign-business
          method: post
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - POST
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent

  analysts_id_unassign-business:
    handler: analysts_id_unassign-business/handler.handler_function
    layers:
      - { Ref: CommonLibLambdaLayer }
    events:
      - http:
          path: analysts/{id}/unassign-business
          method: post
          cors:
            origin: '*'
            methods:
              - POST
            headers:
              - Content-Type
              - Authorization
              - X-Amz-Date
              - X-Amz-Api-Key
              - X-Amz-Security-Token
              - X-Amz-User-Agent
